 class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yia1665702692785.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yia1665702692785.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yia1665702692785.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yia1665702692785\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"yia1665702692785__ulistnew_405644\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create an item list.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"yia1665702692785__topic_d121994e1_d121995e1_d121996e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yia1665702692785_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yia1665702692785__codeblock_prc_51d_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long ulistnew (UHACThAny, UHACT*hList);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yia1665702692785__topic_d86442e1_d86443e1_d86444e1_d86445e1_d86446e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1037130e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"yia1665702692785__parml_ktv_v1d_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hAny</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Any valid handle</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hList</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Handle to the new item list (Output)</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yia1665702692785__topic_d86447e1_d86448e1_d86449e1_d86450e1_d86451e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1037130e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by ulistnew</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__2\">Success. The list was created.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__1\">-165</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__2\">The supplied handle is not valid.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__1\">-1406</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yia1665702692785__table_d14909e1_d14910e1_d14911e1__entry__2\">Memory could not be allocated or freed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yia1665702692785__topic_d86452e1_d86453e1_d86454e1_d86455e1_d86456e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1037130e151\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yia1665702692785__d5956e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucall</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yia1665702692785__topic_d86457e1_d86458e1_d86459e1_d86460e1_d86461e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1037130e163\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yia1665702692785__p_d122021e1_d122022e1_d122023e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ulistnew</code> creates a new item list\n            in which items can be inserted using <code class=\"ph codeph\">ulistput</code>. This list can then be\n            passed to a 4GL operation, as a STRING parameter, and the operation can access the list\n            using the ProcScript functions <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getitem</span> and/or\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">getlistitems</code>. The parameter <var class=\"keyword varname\">hAny</var> can be any valid\n            handle you have in your program (environment handle, instance handle, and so forth).\n            When you are done with a list, you must free it by calling <code class=\"ph codeph\">ufreeh</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yia1665702692785__section_kyk_1bd_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1037130e189\">Example:  ulistnew, ulist2uf, ulistdel, and ulistput</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example creates an associative list, consisting of country\n            codes and names, and passes it to a service, which prints it to the message frame. The\n            operation DOLIST in service TESTSVC is defined as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yia1665702692785_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yia1665702692785__codeblock_uxv_cbd_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation dolist\nparams\nstring thelist : in;\nendparams\nputmess \"%%thelist\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The 3GL code that creates the list and passes it to service DOLIST is as\n            follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yia1665702692785_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yia1665702692785__codeblock_p1r_2bd_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">char *countries[] = {\n\n\"NL\", \"Netherlands\",\n\"GB\", \"Great Britain\",\n\"D\", \"Germany\",\n\"F\", \"France\",\n\"?\", \"huh?\",\n\"I\", \"Italy\",\n\"E\", \"Spain\",\n0 };\n\n#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nvoid pass_itemlist ()\n{\nUHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */\nUHACT hOp; /* Operation handles for OP1 amd OP2 */\nlong actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */\nUHACT hList; /* Item list handle */\nint i; /* Loop variable */\n\nueopen(&amp;hEnv); /* Get environment handle */\nuinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0,\nUDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn, &amp;procErr);/* Instantiate service TESTSVC */\n\nuinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"DOLIST\", 0, &amp;hOp);/* Instantiate operation DOLIST*/\nulistnew(hEnv, &amp;hList); /* Create an item list */\n\nfor ( i=0; countries[i]; i+= 2 ) /* Loop through the data */\n{\nulistput(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0,\ncountries[i], countries[i+1] ); /* Add the list item */\n}\n\nulistdel(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, \"?\");/* Delete the item with id \"?\" */\nulist2uf(hOp, 1, hList); /* Copy item list to operation param*/\nuopract(hOp, &amp;actStatus, &amp;procErr); /* Activate the operation */\n\nuinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Destroy instance */\nufreeh (&amp;hList); /* Free list handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hOp); /* Free operation handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hIn); /* Free instance handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hEnv); /* Free environment handle */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The operation DOLIST prints this line to the message frame</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yia1665702692785_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yia1665702692785__codeblock_srh_gbd_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">NL=Netherlands;GB=Great Britain;D=Germany;F=France;I=Italy;E=Spain</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nci1665702692918.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ulistput</a><p>Insert an item into an item list.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ldz1665702692989.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ustr2uf</a><p>Copy string data from a program buffer to a basic parameter or entity field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534105\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534105\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ulistnew Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Create an item list. Explain this code long ulistnew (UHACThAny, UHACT*hList); Copy Parameters hAny Any valid handle hList Handle to the new item list (Output) Return Values Table 1. Values returned by ulistnew Value Meaning 0 Success. The list was created. -165 The supplied handle is not valid. -1406 Memory could not be allocated or freed. Use Library: ucall Description ulistnew creates a new item list in which items can be inserted using ulistput . This list can then be passed to a 4GL operation, as a STRING parameter, and the operation can access the list using the ProcScript functions getitem and/or getlistitems . The parameter hAny can be any valid handle you have in your program (environment handle, instance handle, and so forth). When you are done with a list, you must free it by calling ufreeh . Example: ulistnew, ulist2uf, ulistdel, and ulistput The following example creates an associative list, consisting of country codes and names, and passes it to a service, which prints it to the message frame. The operation DOLIST in service TESTSVC is defined as follows: Explain this code operation dolist params string thelist : in; endparams putmess \"%%thelist\" end Copy The 3GL code that creates the list and passes it to service DOLIST is as follows: Explain this code char *countries[] = { \"NL\", \"Netherlands\", \"GB\", \"Great Britain\", \"D\", \"Germany\", \"F\", \"France\", \"?\", \"huh?\", \"I\", \"Italy\", \"E\", \"Spain\", 0 }; #include <h3gl.h> void pass_itemlist () { UHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */ UHACT hOp; /* Operation handles for OP1 amd OP2 */ long actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */ UHACT hList; /* Item list handle */ int i; /* Loop variable */ ueopen(&hEnv); /* Get environment handle */ uinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn, &procErr);/* Instantiate service TESTSVC */ uinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"DOLIST\", 0, &hOp);/* Instantiate operation DOLIST*/ ulistnew(hEnv, &hList); /* Create an item list */ for ( i=0; countries[i]; i+= 2 ) /* Loop through the data */ { ulistput(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, countries[i], countries[i+1] ); /* Add the list item */ } ulistdel(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, \"?\");/* Delete the item with id \"?\" */ ulist2uf(hOp, 1, hList); /* Copy item list to operation param*/ uopract(hOp, &actStatus, &procErr); /* Activate the operation */ uinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Destroy instance */ ufreeh (&hList); /* Free list handle */ ufreeh (&hOp); /* Free operation handle */ ufreeh (&hIn); /* Free instance handle */ ufreeh (&hEnv); /* Free environment handle */ } Copy The operation DOLIST prints this line to the message frame Explain this code NL=Netherlands;GB=Great Britain;D=Germany;F=France;I=Italy;E=Spain Copy Related Links ulistput Insert an item into an item list. ustr2uf Copy string data from a program buffer to a basic parameter or entity field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}